Dia. 03 Big Illusion
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par It is a \cf1\b big illusion\cf0\b0  if White thinks he can make pae with White 1 as well.
\par
\par However in the variation Black made a mistake as well.
\par Black 2 is a bad move.
\par After that White plays at 3 and it becomes same with the correct variation.
\par
\par }
